data.description: Welcome to this spacious home in the charming city of Poway, known as the "city in the country". As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a large kitchen boasting a Viking double oven/stove, full-size refrigerator, and freezer, perfect for the culinary enthusiast. The home features two cozy fireplaces, a whole house fan, water filtration system, and owned solar panels, ensuring comfort and energy efficiency year-round. The expansive family room offers ample space for relaxation and entertainment, while two bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms downstairs provide convenience and versatility. Upstairs, the beautiful primary suite awaits, complete with a fireplace and an adjoining room suitable for an office, nursery, or additional bedroom. A bonus room currently utilized as a billiards room presents the exciting potential to be transformed into an ADU, offering a separate living space for in-laws or creating a lucrative rental opportunity. The welcoming front porch is perfect for enjoying stunning sunsets and fostering a sense of community, in a friendly neighborhood. There are 3 backyard sheds for storage and/or workshops and a grilling area. The home is conveniently located near an array of amenities including restaurants, parks, and scenic trails, catering to an active and vibrant lifestyle. With no HOA or Mello-Roos, and part of the esteemed Unified Poway School District, this residence offers both convenience and quality education.
